question: Give me all the articles with photos and videos related to technology.
sql_query1:
SELECT Articles.title 
FROM Articles
WHERE (Articles.visualStorytelling = "Photo" OR Articles.visualStorytelling = "Video") AND Articles.articleType = "Technology"
sql_query2:
SELECT Articles.title 
FROM Articles
WHERE Articles.visualStorytelling = "Photo" OR Articles.visualStorytelling = "Video" AND Articles.articleType = "Technology"
interpretation1: List both articles with photos and articles with videos where any are on the subject of technology.
interpretation2: Show all of the articles with photos, also show the articles with videos but just those about technology.
